{"tid":1473520,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[極限奶共]奧地利水晶品牌SWAROVSKI 連台灣網站都delete埋","createTime":"2019-08-15T01:02:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T03:32:53.000Z","uid":36262,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d749ab582a681d7af702d62574f08cf7a9ab0c13","tid":1473520,"uid":36262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:02:35.000Z","msg":"記者林明瑋 / 綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n「T恤之亂」讓各國際品牌神經緊繃，無奈事件越演越烈，大陸網友不只挖出過去的T恤，更開始肉搜各品牌官網對於國家、地區的分類方式，奧地利水晶品牌SWAROVSKI（施華洛世奇）也中槍，因將中國、台灣、香港並列惹議，實際搜尋發現，施華洛世奇直接將台灣網頁移除，只留下「.cn」也就是大陸網頁，表明立場不手軟。<br />\n<br />\n施華洛世奇今早（8／13）在官方微博發表聲明，表示：「對情感受到傷害的中國人民、無辜受到牽連的各合作單位及亞洲代言人江疏影女士，我們感到萬分抱歉。」江疏影工作室微博在今天上午約11時發出聲明，表示：「已第一時間向施華洛世奇品牌發出解約通知。」<br />\n<br />\n施華洛世奇原有台灣官方網頁（<a href=\"https://www.swarovski.com/zh_TW-TW/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swarovski.com%2Fzh_TW-TW%2F&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=59ec7765\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swarovski.com/zh_TW-TW/</a><br />\n），現已移除，如登入會看到以繁體字通知「親愛的顧客此網頁已被移除，請登入 <a href=\"http://www.swarovski.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.swarovski.com&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=39aae904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.swarovski.com</a> 到訪施華洛世奇網站。 您的施華洛世奇網上團隊」，而簡體字則為「<a href=\"http://請登錄www.swarovski.com.cn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%AB%8B%E7%99%BB%E9%8C%84www.swarovski.com.cn&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=1135f167\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">請登錄www.swarovski.com.cn</a>」，試圖迅速滅火。<br />\n<br />\n施華洛世奇聲明全文如下：<br />\n<br />\n對情感受到傷害的中國人民、無辜受到牽連的各合作單位及亞洲代言人江疏影女士，我們感到萬分抱歉。<br />\n<br />\n施華洛世奇已經在全球加強對中國地區的認知和支持，從而加速以中國市場為核心的自查。施華洛世奇全球在各個國家和地區擁有上千個網站，目前我們在逐一排查，會盡全力在最短時間内糾正錯誤，我們相信用行動彌補才是表達立場最好的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n施華洛世奇從來堅決維護中國的主權和領土完整，為中國市場和人民帶來全球化統一的服務。責任在肩，初心未變。<br />\n<br />\n萬分感謝各界人士監督，施華洛世奇願繼續與中國人民一起共築和諧社會。<br />\n<a href=\"https://fashion.ettoday.net/news/1511828?redirect=1&amp;fbclid=IwAR3oU-G6rz3bS3ktzf6poVO3MTUcqFh1zoYrJTHdXtPAZn56pjtLVs2wvcg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffashion.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1511828%3Fredirect%3D1%26fbclid%3DIwAR3oU-G6rz3bS3ktzf6poVO3MTUcqFh1zoYrJTHdXtPAZn56pjtLVs2wvcg&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=272dc87d\" target=\"_blank\">https://fashion.ettoday.net/news/1511828?redirect=1&amp;fbclid=IwAR3oU-G6rz3bS3ktzf6poVO3MTUcqFh1zoYrJTHdXtPAZn56pjtLVs2wvcg</a><br />\n<br />\n好撚肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242fcf80972dac0ee875ee17e5666f59d1f6b0c1","tid":1473520,"uid":36262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:17:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c27adceee527b4a334ff91ea109394f02da9a3","tid":1473520,"uid":105976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:19:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔撚再買"},{"pid":"d545e9d4404d81a868cd951556f39fab42b8490b","tid":1473520,"uid":45376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:21:03.000Z","msg":"不意外啦<br />\n去奧地利佢啲flagship store睇過陣<br />\n9成支那客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e653c816f8c8cac0db72ae09c758e30c265795","tid":1473520,"uid":36262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33c27adceee527b4a334ff91ea109394f02da9a3","tid":1473520,"uid":105976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:19:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔撚再買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18a38c61d627432687f5eb61126d6469d3fbfd3d","tid":1473520,"uid":143580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6e88d1c5c4fabf5dbd297ca388a6bf56698692","tid":1473520,"uid":109115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d545e9d4404d81a868cd951556f39fab42b8490b","tid":1473520,"uid":45376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:21:03.000Z","msg":"不意外啦<br />\n去奧地利佢啲flagship store睇過陣<br />\n9成支那客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:28:17.000Z","msg":"呢樣真 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f7b9e2427f1682581a864a081cc5c249195ea3","tid":1473520,"uid":251366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:34:51.000Z","msg":"罷買"},{"pid":"d31a34c4ba6509d0aabfe1f4a20cccf7043ce47f","tid":1473520,"uid":85327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:35:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2502d7c3e6f8dc852cbf4b092091a5bf403fd479","tid":1473520,"uid":199838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T23:39:03.000Z","msg":"[b]<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好似無乜人知</span>[b]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GSMpSnb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGSMpSnb.png&h=bcb59e1e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J0A93tR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ0A93tR.jpg&h=0020a5c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ea5ab1d2238159d5263398659593ebaae06dde6","tid":1473520,"uid":289120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T23:45:11.000Z","msg":"太好了 抵制晒佢 睇你抵制得幾多 最好吓鳩走晒啲外資外企"},{"pid":"b797c614e7d50b00e73c7d7f848c9787a4524fdd","tid":1473520,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T00:42:56.000Z","msg":"台灣真係好撚慘<br />\n無喇喇俾人講幾句就就快俾人食埋"},{"pid":"b14ecfaa70ae173a684f4e7ea43df2c606ccb2d9","tid":1473520,"uid":183601,"